   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Adding myself to the cc: list, OpenStack Horizon currently has 6 people who
indicated they want to help but no way to contact them and it'd be awesome to
have a way to let them know! :)

Perhaps in the meantime, it would be possible to show a message to the user
after they click the button? To remind them to check that their profile contains
some way to contact them, and perhaps also thank them for their interest.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
